short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Shows OpenAPI (swagger) yaml/json rendered by redoc. This extension previews github or url

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
openapi yaml/json file shows in the github.com or file tab of your browser to swagger-ui external rendering site(https://redoc-viewer.vercel.app/) in a new tab.

For file views on the github.com site, the login cookie information is used to obtain and display the tokenized URL of the private repository.
